{"tid":1985726,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"剛禁野味即研吃海豚 當局無視教訓","createTime":"2020-04-23T10:43:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-23T14:13:05.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"f2cb8e9c63e6eca1747577b96647cf2b02defa30","tid":1985726,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T10:43:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200423/PJZYAPMNUJQLHKZ7Q3AJEIZO2A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200423%2FPJZYAPMNUJQLHKZ7Q3AJEIZO2A%2F&d=7FLALsszV4LuAMmN05fc6qWONrq76Y1XZ%2F%2BBeLOBzgc%3D&h=7729b330\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200423%2FPJZYAPMNUJQLHKZ7Q3AJEIZO2A%2F&h=14eba07b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200423/PJZYAPMNUJQLHKZ7Q3AJEIZO2A/</a><br />\n<br />\n剛禁野味即研吃海豚 當局無視教訓<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200423/large/1587570545_9951.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200423%2Flarge%2F1587570545_9951.jpg&h=38a6584f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n珠海曾有白海豚被分屍出售。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】「中華白海豚入藥」在中國掀熱議，有評論指因武漢肺炎疫情，中國剛立法禁食野味，現在又提出要把中華白海豚入藥，質疑當局是否「好了傷疤忘了痛」。「廣西海洋藥用資源名錄」網更聲稱，其收錄近700種「海洋藥用生物」，包括易危級別的江豚。本港註冊中醫師指中國《藥典》並無與海豚相關記載。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：華擬研白海豚入藥 與保育背道而馳 曝光後急刪文<br />\n<br />\n中醫師：《藥典》無海豚記載<br />\n<br />\n「廣西海洋藥用資源名錄」網稱，在廣西海洋局、教育廳、科技廳等科研課題支持下，通過多本海洋藥用資源著作資料，網站更有廣西中醫藥大學、廣西北部灣海洋中藥應用技術與產品研發實驗室及廣西中藥藥效研究重點實驗室的連結，但沒有表明是否與這些單位有關係。<br />\n<br />\n本報在該網站以「海豚」搜尋，結果出現六個選項，即該名錄收錄六種海豚具「藥用價值」，當中江豚的功效為「解毒，生肌，鎮痛，殺蟲。主治癩痢頭」。<br />\n<br />\n《新京報》和《光明日報》旗下光明網也刊評論，指在武漢肺炎教訓下居然還想把野生動物用作入藥，「是好了傷疤忘了痛」。本港註冊中醫師余健楚對本報強調，根據《中華人民共和國藥典》，並沒有提到中華白海豚還是其他海豚的藥用價值，質疑有人「張冠李戴、移花接木」，利用中醫名目作宣傳。"},{"pid":"b70c145804723996eae69eb58a87fe720aadf8cb","tid":1985726,"uid":19725,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T10:44:59.000Z","msg":"海豚 = 海既豬<br />\n<br />\n叫中國人唔食？ cls"},{"pid":"ad814674ccb2e67d2d2667e996f97e17d2b5a19f","tid":1985726,"uid":43809,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T10:45:31.000Z","msg":"豚肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9acec4468a7206733839a2f41f3d782478b591bb","tid":1985726,"uid":63934,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T10:47:05.000Z","msg":"依中國人肉算啦"},{"pid":"b336a2bdc151680c355c1786c71cc085b211f343","tid":1985726,"uid":192813,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T10:48:13.000Z","msg":"大陸人真係全世界最on9民族"},{"pid":"eb6ceae2c071c731164c52964dbdcb2ab323b828","tid":1985726,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T10:48:19.000Z","msg":"How dare you"},{"pid":"07de9616a8dd623ae5ac2d3df703c5e0ce29fe70","tid":1985726,"uid":258578,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T10:48:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"64736039cae996753052d7ea6fbdee4d4c9c40ad","tid":1985726,"uid":46896,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T10:48:46.000Z","msg":"海豚係咪背脊向天先？背脊向天嘅即係食得啦"},{"pid":"321eab73ae98155cc17321a88112134940c8f47b","tid":1985726,"uid":99700,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T10:50:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AWOWoc5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAWOWoc5.png&h=1b31c4cb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5d5a18ba994d3c68f01458a30fdf110788e6ad4d","tid":1985726,"uid":152388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T10:51:13.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e33df8bcd7159c537041ccc2ce7876be24221503","tid":1985726,"uid":129733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T10:52:14.000Z","msg":"下次爆發廣西肺炎"},{"pid":"d65d6eb53128cff847d6c2b01b4d38d359b48f1b","tid":1985726,"uid":213142,"lik